@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Khumalo Craft</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-wEmeIV1mKuiNpJSK3siM7k2WKGCL6oHp8KATV7fLSmzP5h5p5DYjKg4ckZo4Nlg" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #343a40;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .about-section {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .about-section p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #6c757d;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .about-section .highlight {
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #007bff;
            }

        .creators {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .creators img {
            width: 150px;
            margin: 0 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <div class="about-section">
            <div class="creators">
                <img src="~/images/jameskhumalo.png" alt="James Khumalo">
                <img src="~/images/kellyclarckson.png" alt="Kelly Clarckson">
                <img src="~/images/tylerwoodley.png" alt="Tyler Woodley">
            </div>
            <p>Welcome to <span class="highlight">Khumalo Craft</span>, your destination for unique, handcrafted products from artisans around the world. Our mission is to connect talented artisans with a discerning audience who appreciates the beauty and craftsmanship of handmade goods.</p>
            <p>Founded by visionary entrepreneur <span class="highlight">James Khumalo</span>, Khumalo Craft is more than just an e-commerce platform – it's a community dedicated to celebrating creativity and supporting independent artisans. We are also proud to collaborate with renowned creators such as <span class="highlight">Kelly Clarckson</span> and <span class="highlight">Tyler Woodley</span>.</p>
            <p>At Khumalo Craft, we strive to provide a user-friendly and accessible platform where artisans can showcase their work and customers can discover one-of-a-kind treasures. With a focus on quality, authenticity, and ethical sourcing, we curate a diverse selection of products that tell a story and make a meaningful impact.</p>
            <p>Join us on our journey to empower artisans, inspire creativity, and foster connections across cultures. Experience the beauty of handmade craftsmanship with Khumalo Craft today!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
